description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 62, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 62, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [62 Votes, Common]
